Title: Part 9: The ships of Umbar
Text: The King of the Dead and his army of dead soldiers of oathbreakers will follow is into the battle against Sauron!Now I have to find the ships of the Umbar Corsairs and take them in our controll. That should be a great surprise to the Orcs at the port of Minas Tirith.
CompleteText: The Umbar pirate captains are defeated! Now I can take the ship and drive to Minas Thirith! I hope it's not to late!
